# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:18
translate chinese tammy14_7a4e2492:

    # "I'm getting ready for bed, in the kitchen filling a glass with water, when the front door suddenly bursts open."
    "我正准备睡觉，在厨房里往杯子里倒水，这时前门突然被猛地推开。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:19
translate chinese tammy14_173b7903:

    # "Tammy and Suzy stomp in, talking loudly."
    "塔米和苏茜气冲冲地闯进来，大声嚷嚷着。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:20
translate chinese tammy14_ac6f9215:

    # tm "... stupid fuck, I'm gonna kick his ass!"
    tm "……那个蠢货，我要揍扁他！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:21
translate chinese tammy14_6284e2b4:

    # ss "You can't do that, baby."
    ss "你不能那样做，宝贝。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:22
translate chinese tammy14_56984c71:

    # tm "Yeah I can. He's bigger, but I can take him down and break his arm."
    tm "能啊。他个头虽然大，但我能把他放倒，再掰断他的胳膊。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:23
translate chinese tammy14_37a2cc30:

    # ss "No, I mean you can't, you'll go to jail."
    ss "不，我是说你不能，你会进监狱的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:24
translate chinese tammy14_08d01644:

    # tm "I don't care! {i}He{/i} should be in jail!"
    tm "我才不管呢！{i}他{/i}就该进监狱！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:27
translate chinese tammy14_1c2669de:

    # ss "I know, but you can't do anything about that."
    ss "我知道，但这事你也没办法。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:28
translate chinese tammy14_98f83cc0:

    # tm "I just don't know what to do. I can't go back there."
    tm "我真的不知道该怎么办。我不能再回去那里了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:31
translate chinese tammy14_7704ce42:

    # sp "Is everything okay?"
    sp "一切都还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:32
translate chinese tammy14_dbcf64d2:

    # ss "Her step-dad is being awful again."
    ss "她的继父又在胡闹了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:33
translate chinese tammy14_c999da2a:

    # tm "I'm sorry if I woke you up, Lisa. We'll be quieter."
    tm "丽莎，如果吵醒你了，真抱歉。我们会小声点的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:36
translate chinese tammy14_34283699:

    # sp "Oh, no honey, I just want to make sure you're okay."
    sp "哦，不，亲爱的，我只是想确认你没事。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:37
translate chinese tammy14_cf7fba88:

    # sp "Are you okay?"
    sp "你还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:38
translate chinese tammy14_71ed8e31:

    # "At that point, Tammy's tough exterior shatters."
    "那一刻，塔米的坚强外表崩塌了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:42
translate chinese tammy14_4c6ab0b0:

    # tm "No, I'm not okay."
    tm "不，我不好。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:43
translate chinese tammy14_8a3ebac6:

    # tm "I wish my mom would leave him, but I don't know if she ever will."
    tm "真希望我妈妈能离开他，但我不知道她会不会这么做。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:44
translate chinese tammy14_ceb95749:

    # tm "He's so awful. I don't ever want to go back there."
    tm "他太糟糕了。我再也不想回去那里了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:45
translate chinese tammy14_b95023cd:

    # ss "I've been telling her that she can move in with us, Mom."
    ss "“我一直跟妈妈说，她可以搬来跟我们住，妈妈。”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:48
translate chinese tammy14_6d319373:

    # sp "You should, honey. You need to get out of that environment."
    sp "“你应该搬来的，亲爱的。你得离开那个环境。”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:49
translate chinese tammy14_3fad3cef:

    # sp "You could stay in Suzy's room, or you could set up down in the basement, if you'd rather have your own space."
    sp "“你可以住苏茜的房间，或者如果你想要自己的空间，也可以在地下室安顿下来。”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:50
translate chinese tammy14_2f672715:

    # sp "Either way, we'd love to have you here."
    sp "“无论哪种方式，我们都很欢迎你住在这里。”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:51
translate chinese tammy14_1c64185f:

    # tm "Really? I wouldn't be a burden?"
    tm "真的吗？我不会给你们添麻烦吧？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:52
translate chinese tammy14_08156915:

    # sp "No, honey, you'd never be a burden. I love you."
    sp "不，亲爱的，你永远不会是负担。我爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:55
translate chinese tammy14_24587f81:

    # tm "God, I wish you were my mom. You're the best ever."
    tm "天啊，真希望你是我亲妈。你真是最棒的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:56
translate chinese tammy14_6511bc47:

    # sp "I've made my share of mistakes too. It's hard to get out of them sometimes."
    sp "我也犯过不少错。有时候很难摆脱那些阴影。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:57
translate chinese tammy14_80ccefda:

    # sp "Hopefully your mom will come around eventually."
    sp "希望你妈妈最终能回心转意。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:58
translate chinese tammy14_4207618e:

    # sp "Until then, why don't you stay here, please?"
    sp "在那之前，你就先住在这里吧，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:61
translate chinese tammy14_457c6c40:

    # tm "You're serious, then?"
    tm "你是认真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:62
translate chinese tammy14_11137790:

    # sp "Absolutely."
    sp "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:65
translate chinese tammy14_b63b6db1:

    # tm "And you two don't mind? I won't be getting in the way here?"
    tm "你们俩不介意吗？我不会给你们添麻烦吧？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:66
translate chinese tammy14_2a08fdcb:

    # ss "Of course not, dummy! I've been trying to get you to move in for months!"
    ss "当然不，傻瓜！我已经想让你搬过来好几个月了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:67
translate chinese tammy14_68c0a7e7:

    # pc "I don't mind at all."
    pc "我一点都不介意。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:68
translate chinese tammy14_0ba1ce31:

    # tm "Okay. I'll move in."
    tm "好吧。我就搬过来。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:69
translate chinese tammy14_8d935799:

    # tm "Just for a while. Until things settle down."
    tm "只是暂时住住。等事情安定下来。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:70
translate chinese tammy14_7b787768:

    # sp "However long you need, honey."
    sp "无论你需要多久，亲爱的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:73
translate chinese tammy14_a723e4f9:

    # tm "Thank you so much!"
    tm "太感谢你了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:74
translate chinese tammy14_5cee14df:

    # tm "I'll go get my stuff tomorrow while he's at work. There's not much."
    tm "明天他上班的时候，我去把东西搬过来。东西不多。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:75
translate chinese tammy14_c31d0d41:

    # tm "And I'll pay you rent too."
    tm "房租我也会付的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:76
translate chinese tammy14_380d34b5:

    # sp "That's not necessary. Save your money, okay?"
    sp "没那个必要。省着点钱，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:77
translate chinese tammy14_03746258:

    # sp "Just focus on yourself for a while."
    sp "先把自己的事处理好再说。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:79
translate chinese tammy14_01c8cdc6:

    # "I know that Lisa is struggling to pay all the bills. Even then, she wouldn't accept payment for helping Tammy."
    "我知道丽莎为了付账单已经很吃力了。即便如此，她还是不肯收塔米的房租。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:80
translate chinese tammy14_423f725c:

    # "It just isn't in her nature."
    "这根本不是她的作风。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:82
translate chinese tammy14_06e37fea:

    # "With all the money in the safe, Lisa would not have to worry about bills anymore. At least, not for a long time."
    "有了保险箱里的钱，丽莎就不用再为账单发愁了。至少，在很长一段时间内不用担心。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:85
translate chinese tammy14_a7518ba2:

    # sp "Now, I have to get to bed. Work in the morning."
    sp "现在，我得去睡觉了。明天早上还要上班。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:86
translate chinese tammy14_6bfe5e7b:

    # sp "Let me know if you need anything though."
    sp "不过，如果你需要什么，随时告诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:87
translate chinese tammy14_2d169360:

    # tm "Okay. Thanks again, Lisa."
    tm "好的。再次感谢你，丽莎。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:88
translate chinese tammy14_dfbbd1a7:

    # sp "Good night, you three."
    sp "晚安，你们三个。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:89
translate chinese tammy14_092737ee:

    # ss "Good night, Mom!"
    ss "晚安，妈妈！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:90
translate chinese tammy14_ffdf8a5b:

    # tm "Good night, Mom!"
    tm "晚安，妈妈！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:91
translate chinese tammy14_da82243e:

    # pc "Good night, [mom]!"
    pc "晚安，[mom]！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:94
translate chinese tammy14_d79ef8d0:

    # tm "Well, I guess you got a new roommate."
    tm "呃，看来你有了新室友。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:95
translate chinese tammy14_d9ac07ff:

    # ss "Yay! I'm so glad you finally gave in!"
    ss "太好啦！真高兴你终于妥协了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:96
translate chinese tammy14_a522539f:

    # ss "Do you feel a little better now?"
    ss "现在感觉好一点了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:97
translate chinese tammy14_282d6942:

    # tm "A little, yeah. Your mom is so nice."
    tm "好一点了，嗯。你妈妈真好。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:98
translate chinese tammy14_13fb3cd3:

    # pc "Do you want to talk about what happened?"
    pc "想聊聊刚才发生的事吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:101
translate chinese tammy14_9bd84187:

    # tm "Ugh, not really. Just my step-dad being a toolbag again."
    tm "唉，不想。就是我继父又耍混蛋了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:102
translate chinese tammy14_a309b747:

    # ss "One of his friends saw me and Tammy kissing at the ice cream parlor the other day and told him."
    ss "前几天他有个朋友在冰淇淋店看到我和塔米接吻，然后告诉了他。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:103
translate chinese tammy14_7b955f80:

    # ss "And now he's gone all strict mode, calling her names and yelling at her mom for \"raising a dyke.\""
    ss "现在他突然变得特别严厉，不仅骂我，还冲我妈大吼大叫，说她“养了个女同”。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:104
translate chinese tammy14_9d57193f:

    # pc "Fuck, that's awful. I'm sorry."
    pc "靠，太糟糕了。真抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:105
translate chinese tammy14_9f68ab72:

    # tm "It's fine. I don't care if he calls me names. But he treats my mom like shit too and she just takes it."
    tm "没关系。他骂我我不在乎。但他对妈妈也特别差，而她总是默默忍受。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:106
translate chinese tammy14_d9857395:

    # tm "And I got fed up with it tonight and got in his face."
    tm "今晚我实在受够了，直接冲他发火。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:109
translate chinese tammy14_c6134a41:

    # tm "He actually put his hands on me. I didn't mean to, but I reacted by putting him in an armbar."
    tm "他居然动手打我。我本来没那个意思，但下意识就用臂绞锁住了他。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:110
translate chinese tammy14_050d517c:

    # tm "Then my mom hit me and yelled at me to get off of him... so I let him go."
    tm "然后我妈打了我一巴掌，大喊让我放开他……所以我放开了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:111
translate chinese tammy14_087ad477:

    # tm "And I left."
    tm "然后我就走了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:112
translate chinese tammy14_14e5199b:

    # tm "I should have broke his fucking arm."
    tm "我真该掰断他那该死的手臂。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:113
translate chinese tammy14_33602524:

    # ss "No, you shouldn't have. You did good."
    ss "不，你不该那样做。你做得很好。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:114
translate chinese tammy14_7e6cd6fb:

    # tm "It was so hard to hold back."
    tm "当时真的很难克制自己。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:115
translate chinese tammy14_823afdc5:

    # pc "I'm sorry you're having to deal with all that. That sucks."
    pc "很抱歉你得经历这些。真倒霉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:116
translate chinese tammy14_1bc3d8ea:

    # pc "If I could help with anything, you just have to ask, you know?"
    pc "如果我能帮上什么忙，你尽管开口，知道吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:119
translate chinese tammy14_db58cf54:

    # tm "Want to make some popcorn? I kinda want to just chill and watch a movie or something."
    tm "想吃点爆米花吗？我有点想放松一下，看个电影什么的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:120
translate chinese tammy14_230676b3:

    # pc "I think I can manage that."
    pc "我觉得我能搞定。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:123
translate chinese tammy14_7fcae3d7:

    # "I go to the kitchen and make us a big bowl of popcorn and some drinks."
    "我走进厨房，给我们做了一大碗爆米花和几杯饮料。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:126
translate chinese tammy14_8774a9ea:

    # "And a few minutes later, we sit together on the couch, watching a movie."
    "几分钟后，我们并排坐在沙发上，一起看电影。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:127
translate chinese tammy14_8e0bf432:

    # ss "What is this anyway? The acting is so bad."
    ss "这到底是什么片子啊？演技太烂了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:128
translate chinese tammy14_4a5effb9:

    # tm "We're not watching it for the acting. We're watching it because Donnie Yen and Cynthia Khan are badasses."
    tm "我们又不是冲着演技看的。我们看是因为甄子丹和陈嘉桦太酷了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:129
translate chinese tammy14_1915a42f:

    # ss "Could they be badasses who can act?"
    ss "难道他们不能既酷又能演戏吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:132
translate chinese tammy14_636b6f2c:

    # tm "Donnie Yen can act! We watched Ip Man, remember?"
    tm "甄子丹会演戏的！我们看过《叶问》，记得吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:133
translate chinese tammy14_f27e8653:

    # ss "Is that the one with the guy who fought with the big caligraphy brush?"
    ss "就是那个和拿着大毛笔的人打架的片子吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:134
translate chinese tammy14_17b93ba5:

    # tm "No, that was Tony Leung in Hero. Donnie Yen was in that too though. He had that badass fight in the courtyard with Jet Li."
    tm "不，那是梁朝伟在《英雄》里的戏。不过甄子丹也在那部里。他在庭院里和李连杰那场打斗简直酷毙了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:135
translate chinese tammy14_00ddbddc:

    # ss "I don't remember. The acting in that one was pretty good though."
    ss "我不记得了。不过那部电影的演技还挺不错的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:138
translate chinese tammy14_b5dbc1b2:

    # "We eat popcorn and chat and cuddle throughout the whole movie."
    "整部电影期间，我们一边吃爆米花，一边聊天，还互相依偎着。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:139
translate chinese tammy14_7e9fe87d:

    # "It's nice to just spend time with the girls and relax. I think Tammy needed that."
    "能和女孩们一起度过这段放松的时光真好。我觉得谭米很需要这样。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:140
translate chinese tammy14_6459b26b:

    # "By the time the movie is over, all three of us are tired and ready for bed."
    "电影结束时，我们三个人都累了，准备睡觉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:143
translate chinese tammy14_f0ea57e0:

    # "Sleeping arrangements are not even discussed. All three of us go to my bed together."
    "连睡哪里都没商量。我们三个人一起钻进我的被窝。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:144
translate chinese tammy14_8f8ef515:

    # "Both Suzy and I wrap our arms around Tammy, holding her close."
    "我和苏西都搂着塔米，紧紧抱住她。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:145
translate chinese tammy14_ca686a0f:

    # ss "You know you're loved, right?"
    ss "你知道大家都很爱你，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:146
translate chinese tammy14_dda6128b:

    # tm "Yeah. I love you too."
    tm "嗯。我也爱你们。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:147
translate chinese tammy14_02e5361e:

    # tm "Both of you."
    tm "你们两个。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:148
translate chinese tammy14_5346a3b9:

    # tm "Thanks for tonight."
    tm "谢谢你们今晚的陪伴。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:151
translate chinese tammy14_b5ba8a4e:

    # pc "Any time you need anything, I'll be here for you."
    pc "无论什么时候，只要你需要，我都会在这里。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:152
translate chinese tammy14_68ef5b0d:

    # tm "Thanks, [pcname]. Really."
    tm "谢谢，[pcname]。真的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:153
translate chinese tammy14_450f2c68:

    # tm "You guys mean the world to me."
    tm "你们对我来说就是全世界。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:156
translate chinese tammy14_0aaa364a:

    # tm "Ahh! You're squishing me!"
    tm "啊！你把我挤扁了！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:157
translate chinese tammy14_ee137836:

    # ss "Good! Squish her, [bro]! Squish her!"
    ss "好！挤她，[bro]！挤她！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:158
translate chinese tammy14_c86d70b8:

    # tm "You're such a dork! I'm going to pinch your nipples off!"
    tm "你真是个傻瓜！我要掐掉你的乳头！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:159
translate chinese tammy14_08d29a8b:

    # ss "Don't threaten me with a good time!"
    ss "别用快乐来威胁我！"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:162
translate chinese tammy14_3ce42e73:

    # tm "Haha, I'm too tired for this right now."
    tm "哈哈，我现在太累了，没精力应付这个。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:163
translate chinese tammy14_a37cc2d4:

    # ss "Yeah, me too."
    ss "是啊，我也是。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:166
translate chinese tammy14_7019ac31:

    # tm "But there will be plenty of chances for us to mess around with me living here now, I guess."
    tm "不过既然我现在住在这里，我想我们以后会有很多机会胡闹的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:167
translate chinese tammy14_ebcc9f51:

    # ss "It's so sexy, all three of us being able to sleep together like this any night we want to."
    ss "我们三个人想睡哪天就睡哪天，能这样睡在一起，真是太性感了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:168
translate chinese tammy14_494fc97b:

    # pc "Yeah, it's amazing."
    pc "是啊，太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:171
translate chinese tammy14_e8b49386:

    # "It doesn't take long, lying like that, for Tammy to fall asleep."
    "就这样躺着没多久，塔米就睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:172
translate chinese tammy14_815d66b7:

    # "And as soon as she's asleep, she immediately begins snoring loudly."
    "一睡着，她立刻就开始打响亮的鼾声。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:175
translate chinese tammy14_055d080f:

    # ss "Dang, she's loud, huh?"
    ss "天啊，她鼾声真大，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:176
translate chinese tammy14_593f6724:

    # "I nod, trying to stay quiet."
    "我点点头，尽量保持安静。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:177
translate chinese tammy14_536bf33b:

    # ss "When she's really tired like this, she passes out hard. You could shake her and she's not going to wake up."
    ss "她像这样累坏了的时候，睡得特别沉。就算摇她也不会醒。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:178
translate chinese tammy14_20e84dbf:

    # pc "She deserves a good night sleep."
    pc "她值得睡个好觉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:179
translate chinese tammy14_e51a7dc2:

    # ss "Yeah. Thanks for being a good boyfriend tonight, [bro]."
    ss "是啊。谢谢你今晚当了个好男朋友，[bro]。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:180
translate chinese tammy14_a248948f:

    # pc "Of course."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:181
translate chinese tammy14_53a16996:

    # ss "Love you."
    ss "爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:182
translate chinese tammy14_3213fe29:

    # pc "Love you too, [sis]."
    pc "我也爱你，[sis]。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:185
translate chinese tammy14_87d1006f:

    # "Suzy lies back down again and falls asleep."
    "苏茜又躺下睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:188
translate chinese tammy14_da5d00b9:

    # "Shortly after, despite Tammy's loud snoring, I fall asleep too."
    "没过多久，尽管塔米鼾声如雷，我也睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:189
translate chinese tammy14_2af8e2e3:

    # "I have great dreams all night, but somehow they don't even compare to my waking life."
    "整晚我做着美梦，但不知为何，那些梦根本比不上我的现实生活。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:192
translate chinese tammy14_d8050fd9:

    # "I must have slept hard as well, because I don't wake up through the entire night."
    "我肯定也睡得很沉，因为整晚都没醒过。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:195
translate chinese tammy14_6e97274e:

    # "And when I look around in the morning, they are both gone."
    "早上环顾四周时，她们俩都不见了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:201
translate chinese tammy14_d1a14932:

    # "I get up and go to the bathroom, then walk downstairs."
    "我起身去了一趟洗手间，然后下楼。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:204
translate chinese tammy14_7279822b:

    # "In the dining room, Suzy greets me with a kiss."
    "在餐厅里，苏茜用一个吻向我问好。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:205
translate chinese tammy14_ce46d3ed:

    # ss "There's some breakfast in the kitchen if you want any. Mom made way too much before she left."
    ss "厨房里还有些早餐，如果你想吃的话。妈妈走之前做得实在太多了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:206
translate chinese tammy14_03e500eb:

    # pc "Where's Tammy?"
    pc "塔米去哪儿了？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:207
translate chinese tammy14_6a080cce:

    # ss "She had to leave early for work. I doubt we'll be seeing her for breakfast very often."
    ss "她得早点去上班。我想我们以后很少能和她一起吃早餐了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:208
translate chinese tammy14_34f75a54:

    # pc "Oh, okay."
    pc "哦，好的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:211
translate chinese tammy14_eef7b49f:

    # ss "Did you want to eat breakfast with me... or maybe mess around some?"
    ss "你想跟我一起吃早餐……还是想玩会儿？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:215
translate chinese tammy14_6ae50746:

    # ss "Oh, alright then."
    ss "哦，那好吧。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:218
translate chinese tammy14_b9e9893b:

    # ss "I was hoping you would say that."
    ss "我就盼着你这么说呢。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy14.rpy:222
translate chinese tammy14_ca91b2cf:

    # ss "Oh, okay. See you later then, [bro]."
    ss "哦，好的。那待会儿见，[bro]。"

